According to the Texas Department of Public Safety, she is being treated as a kidnapped child, which has issued an AMBER Alert.

item.title: Who Is Kevin Federlines Wife Victoria Prince?
item.description: Victoria Prince is the wife of Kevin Federline, the American rapper, dancer, DJ, and ex-husband of Britney Spears. Prince and Federline began their relationship in 2008 following the latter’s split and divorce from Spears. Many expected their romance to fizzle out with time, but they surprised the naysayers. The couple dated for about five years before tying the knot in Las Vegas in August 2013. It has been several years down the line, and the couple remains together.
